---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About Us | Atherton & Co" description="Learn about Atherton & Co, a small accounting firm dedicated to providing clear, honest financial guidance for individuals and small businesses.">
  <!-- About Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        About Atherton & Co
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We're a small team with big hearts for helping people make sense of their finances.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-6">
        <p>
          Atherton & Co was founded with a simple belief: accounting shouldn't be intimidating. Too many people dread tax season, avoid looking at their books, or feel lost when it comes to financial decisions—not because they're incapable, but because the industry has made things unnecessarily complicated.
        </p>
        <p>
          We started this firm to change that. Our founders spent years working at larger accounting firms and saw firsthand how clients were often left confused by jargon, surprised by fees, and treated like numbers rather than people. We knew there had to be a better way.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, Atherton & Co serves individuals and small businesses who want a partner, not just a service provider. We take the time to understand your unique situation, explain things in plain English, and provide guidance that actually makes sense for your life and goals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Believe Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What We Believe</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-6">
        <p>
          <strong>Transparency comes first.</strong> We believe you deserve to know exactly what you're paying for and why. No hidden fees, no surprise charges, no fine print. When we quote a price, that's the price—and if anything changes, we'll discuss it with you before moving forward.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Relationships matter.</strong> We're not interested in being a faceless firm that processes your paperwork. We want to know your name, understand your business, and be someone you can call when you have questions. Our clients become part of our community.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Knowledge should be shared.</strong> We don't believe in keeping you in the dark so you'll always need us. Instead, we take the time to educate you about your finances, explain our recommendations, and empower you to make informed decisions. An informed client is our best client.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Choose Atherton & Co</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-6">
        <p>
          When you work with us, you're not just getting an accountant—you're getting a dedicated team that genuinely cares about your financial wellbeing. We handle everything from tax preparation and bookkeeping to financial planning and business advisory services.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're a freelancer trying to navigate quarterly taxes for the first time, a small business owner looking to grow sustainably, or an individual planning for retirement, we're here to help you every step of the way.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ready to experience accounting that actually makes sense? We'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block bg-slate-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors"
        >
          Get in touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
